/**
 * Objective: Explain to compiler how to get to the bathroom
 * Initial data: sitting on the chair
 * Available commands: 
 *      get up, 
        move forward, 
        turn left, 
        turn right, 
        move backward, 
        sit down, 
        door open, 
        door close,
        move upstairs,
        move downstairs
 * Step: Get up
 * Step: move forward x3
 * Step: turn left
 * Step: move upstairs x8
 * Step: turn right
 * Step: door open
 * Step: move forward
 * Step: door close

 * Comment: This set of functions can be further decomposed in some simple items.
 */